item.title: CVE-2021-42063|2024-08-04T03:22:25.975Z -- sap%20se -- sap%20knowledge%20warehouse
item.description: A security vulnerability has been discovered in the SAP Knowledge Warehouse - versions 7.30, 7.31, 7.40, 7.50. The usage of one SAP KW component within a Web browser enables unauthorized attackers to conduct XSS attacks, which might lead to disclose sensitive data.
